conn = pymysql.connect(charset='utf8', **self.databases[0])
self.safe_create_table(conn, u'heiße', u'create table heiße (name varchar(32))'
    )
c = conn.cursor()
c.execute(u"insert into heiße (name) values ('Pißata')")
c.execute(u'select name from heiße')
self.assertEqual(u'Pißata', c.fetchone()[0])
